	<div style="text-align:right;">
		PEDROSO, Caroline Martins<sup>1</sup>; TRAPP, Altemir<sup>2</sup>; OKUMURA, Maria Lucia Miyake<sup>3</sup>; FRANCESCONI, Tiago<sup>4</sup>; CANCIGLIERI JUNIOR, Osiris<sup>5</sup>		<BR>
